// compiler/src/llvm/expression_lowering/native/statement.sfn
//
// Statement lowering and type mapping for LLVM backend.
//
// Implements statement-level lowering (`lower_expression_statement`,
// `lower_return_instruction`), "assignment"/"let" parsing, parameter preparation,
// type annotation mapping to LLVM types (`map_local_type`, `map_return_type`),
// and suspension conflict detection for async code.

